"the database."
msgstr ""
"要查看黑名单号码的完整清单，请导航至 :menuselection:`短信营销应用程序 --> 配置 --> 已拉黑电话号码` "
"查看仪表板，其中包含数据库中所有黑名单电话号码。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/essentials/mailing_lists_blacklists.rst-1
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/essentials/mailing_lists_blacklists.rst-1
