"短信价格取决于接收地和短信长度（字符数）。要查看**每个国家的价格，请查阅**： `Odoo 短信 - 常见问题解答 <https://iap-"
"services.odoo.com/iap/sms/pricing#sms_faq_01>`_。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/pricing/pricing_and_faq.rst:40
