msgid "**Can I send as many SMSs I want at once?**"
msgstr " **可以一次性发送大量的短信吗？**"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/pricing/pricing_and_faq.rst:0
msgid "Yes, if you have enough credits."
